Revenue Pivot
MEDIUM
For each product, show total revenue split into 'Online' and 'Offline' channels as separate columns.

▼
TABLE SCHEMA — click to view
sales( product TEXT, channel TEXT, revenue REAL )
Sample Input
product	channel	revenue
Laptop	Online	500
Laptop	Offline	300
Phone	Online	400
Phone	Online	200
Phone	Offline	100
Expected Output
product	online_revenue	offline_revenue
Laptop	500	300
Phone	600	100


SELECT product,
SUM(CASE WHEN channel='Online' THEN revenue ELSE 0 END) AS online_revenue,
SUM(CASE WHEN channel='Offline' THEN revenue ELSE 0 END) AS offline_revenue
FROM sales
GROUP BY product

This is a classic pivot — use CASE inside SUM to route each row to the right column.
